Cediranib in patients with alveolar soft-part sarcoma (CASPS): a double-blind, 
placebo-controlled, randomised, phase 2 trial.

Judson I(1), Morden JP(2), Kilburn L(2), Leahy M(3), Benson C(4), Bhadri V(5), 
Campbell-Hewson Q(6), Cubedo R(7), Dangoor A(8), Fox L(2), Hennig I(9), Jarman 
K(2), Joubert W(10), Kernaghan S(2), López Pousa A(11), McNeil C(5), Seddon 
