Melanoma patients with additional primary cancers: a single-center retrospective 
analysis.

Dimitriou F(1), Mangana J(1), Curioni-Fontecedro A(2)(3), Rechsteiner M(4), 
Turko P(1), Braun RP(1)(3), Dummer R(#)(1)(3), Cheng PF(#)(1).

Author information:
